{"tid":2027272,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"本港增8宗新型肺炎輸入或相關個案 39日來單日最多","createTime":"2020-05-21T10:45:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T13:00:59.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fdda32c81f50454e4337d4c6cfb6df9bc9f4d02a","tid":2027272,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:45:54.000Z","msg":"本港增8宗新型肺炎輸入或相關個案 39日來單日最多<br />\n2020-05-21 HKT 18:20<br />\n<br />\n本港新增8宗新型肺炎輸入或相關個案，至少4人無病徵，今次是過去39日以來，單日錄得最多確診宗數，至今累計1063宗確診個案。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心表示，已有措施防止個案傳入本地，個別日子有較多個案，不一定對本地情況有特別影響。<br />\n<br />\n就梨木樹群組個案，中心已取得2100多個相關檢測結果，至今全部都是陰性。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1527517-20200521.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1527517-20200521.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=%2FbZU6AtRr1oB2SY8YhhoVy3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=c04b8f79\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1527517-20200521.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=f7d8893e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1527517-20200521.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"a5d31b842d2938057d205601152d025fd3652e8e","tid":2027272,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:47:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ca9cdbb22f0b22f48caff3a4f9a45bf4d6edfc9","tid":2027272,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T13:00:59.000Z","msg":"無本地個案<br />\n周末可以瘋狂出街聚餐消費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}